== 薪酬 ==
芝加哥警局的警员起薪为$43,104，在一年后涨到$55,723，18个月后则为$58,896。如果提升到特殊岗位或领导岗位，基本工资还会随着上涨。除了薪水以外，还有每年$2,920的工作奖金以及$1,800的制服津贴。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.chicagopolice.org/recruitment/recruitment.html|title=A Career with a Future|publisher=Chicago Police Department|accessdate=2007-04-22|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070430060137/http://www.chicagopolice.org/recruitment/recruitment.html|archivedate=2007-04-30}}</ref>

